      "I'm a Sound Engineer currently employed as a Broadcasting Engineering Supervisor at KAN — the Israeli Public Broadcasting Corporation in Jerusalem. In 2016 I graduated with a BA (Hons) in Sound Technology from LIPA (Liverpool Institute for Performing Arts, UK).",
